quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  14,42,Wa Lā Taĥsabanna Allāha Ghāfilāan `Ammā Ya`malu Až-Žālimūna 'Innamā Yu'uakhkhiruhum Liyawmin Tashkhaşu Fīhi Al-'Abşāru
  14,43,Muhţi`īna Muqni`ī Ru'ūsihim Lā Yartaddu 'Ilayhim Ţarfuhum Wa 'Af'idatuhum Hawā'un
  14,44,Wa 'Andhiri An-Nāsa Yawma Ya'tīhimu Al-`Adhābu Fayaqūlu Al-Ladhīna Žalamū Rabbanā 'Akhkhirnā 'Ilá 'Ajalin Qarībin Nujib Da`wataka Wa Nattabi`i Ar-Rusula 'Awalam Takūnū 'Aqsamtum Min Qablu Mā Lakum Min Zawālin
  14,45,Wa Sakantum Fī Masākini Al-Ladhīna Žalamū 'Anfusahum Wa Tabayyana Lakum Kayfa Fa`alnā Bihim Wa Đarabnā Lakumu Al-'Amthāla
  14,46,Wa Qad Makarū Makrahum Wa `Inda Allāhi Makruhum Wa 'In Kāna Makruhum Litazūla Minhu Al-Jibālu
  14,47,Falā Taĥsabanna Allāha Mukhlifa Wa`dihi Rusulahu 'Inna Allāha `Azīzun Dhū Antiqāmin
  14,48,Yawma Tubaddalu Al-'Arđu Ghayra Al-'Arđi Wa As-Samāwātu Wa Barazū Lillāhi Al-Wāĥidi Al-Qahhāri
  14,49,Wa Tará Al-Mujrimīna Yawma'idhin Muqarranīna Fī Al-'Aşfādi
  14,50,Sarābīluhum Min Qaţirānin Wa Taghshá Wujūhahumu An-Nāru
  14,51,Liyajziya Allāhu Kulla Nafsin Mā Kasabat 'Inna Allāha Sarī`u Al-Ĥisābi
  14,52,Hādhā Balāghun Lilnnāsi Wa Liyundharū Bihi Wa Liya`lamū 'Annamā Huwa 'Ilahun Wāĥidun Wa Liyadhakkara 'Ūlū Al-'Albābi